{"tid":646334,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"好想裸辭，連登有冇成功例子","createTime":"2018-04-29T03:00:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-29T09:28:59.000Z","uid":46938,"like":71,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"9f568cbf4f77d87319f120fed5be8c7f8ea92132","tid":646334,"uid":46938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T03:00:36.000Z","msg":"好大壓力好大壓力好大壓力<br />\n<br />\n除了做野辛苦，仲無哂私人時間<br />\n<br />\n平日放工食完飯就要返歸訓教<br />\n<br />\n每日訓6個鐘，仲要晨咁早起身<br />\n<br />\n放假都只係想係屋企訓教<br />\n<br />\n訓夠8個鐘是夢想<br />\n<br />\n好攰好攰好攰<br />\n<br />\n有冇人明我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  炒老細魷魚，做浪子<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  連登仔係鐵人唔撚洗訓，繼續做狗啦你"},{"pid":"cfec9b7384960e1417e6dd1a19609bfd6b04f7d2","tid":646334,"uid":5178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T03:01:41.000Z","msg":"audit?"},{"pid":"7762ccba4fae489253aa20405f38ff8d3df3bc12","tid":646334,"uid":50744,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T03:02:00.000Z","msg":"點為之成功先<br />\n唔等錢洗咪走啦"},{"pid":"036736d6f5f5ac54030d0b0ea8f832ce674737e0","tid":646334,"uid":156326,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T03:02:02.000Z","msg":"幾大 點解咁都搞個投票"},{"pid":"bb736a276bc63a9b021f7ed8aaf8927f3f0fedf6","tid":646334,"uid":66945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T03:03:26.000Z","msg":"搵過份啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就係你呢啲人甘願做奴隸先搞到香港辦公文化咁撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5212ddeccc983c56e6df1f7235165caed4b14d68","tid":646334,"uid":46938,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"cfec9b7384960e1417e6dd1a19609bfd6b04f7d2","tid":646334,"uid":5178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"20